Class to handle geocoding and reverse-geocoding events. API requests may be built from human-readable address to be geocoded into coordinates, or Coordinates can be used to build a call in order to find A human-readable address. Can create class without address or coordinates, but is advised to create them by including parameters: 1. A single (String) Address or 2. A set of two coordinates (String) Longitude and (String) Latitude
